@startuml SC-41-Analytics-RH
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Voir Analytics RH (Client)

object Client
object "Interface Analytics" as InterfaceAnalytics
object "Service Analytics" as ServiceAnalytics
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Service Audit" as ServiceAudit

Client --> InterfaceAnalytics : 1: acceder("Analytics RH")
InterfaceAnalytics --> ServiceAnalytics : 2: obtenirAnalyticsRH(clientId, {periode})
ServiceAnalytics --> BaseDonnees : 3: executerRequete(analytics)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceAnalytics : 3.1: donneeAnalytics

ServiceAnalytics --> ServiceAudit : 3.2: enregistrerAction("ANALYTICS_RH_CONSULTES")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 3.3: sauvegarderLog()

ServiceAnalytics --> InterfaceAnalytics : 4: afficher(graphiques)
InterfaceAnalytics --> Client : 4.1: montrer(insights)

note right of ServiceAnalytics
Analytics RH:
- Tendances effectifs
- Couts paie
- Turnover
- Performance paie
- Tendances absences
end note

@enduml
